OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny intervals along
OL,7,Fwith a few showers. Showers will be
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy, especially across
OL,9,Fthe west. Colder than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late brightness this
OL,12,Fevening and a few showers. Becoming
OL,13,Fdry with clear periods overnight
OL,14,Facross all parts. A cold night with a
OL,15,Fslight frost in sheltered glens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
