OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry morning with some early
OL,6,Fbrightness. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fwill spread northeast in the afternoon
OL,8,Fand evening. Becoming windy with
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly gales along exposed
OL,10,Fcoasts in the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,13,Fintervals and the chance of a few
OL,14,Fshowers on Saturday, but some dry
OL,15,Fweather too. More in the way of
OL,16,Fshowers on Sunday and Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
